name: Cookie Cutter (itch)
description:
What happens in the gingerbread house while the witch is not at home? Who is the last gingerbread standing and end up ruling the sweetness?

The game is inspired by a fairytale "Hansel and Gretel"

Special thanks to Keppu for technical help and playtesting
